******************************
*****
*****  BCPL PROGRAMMING  *****
*****
******************************

BCPL was created by Martin Richards at Cambridge University in 1967. It is a very basic
"keep it simple" computer programming language that influenced later computer programming
languages such as C and C++.


Links:

https://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/~mr10/BCPL.html
https://www.nordier.com/
https://rosettacode.org/wiki/Category:BCPL
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BCPL


